{"tid":1332930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持對家加藤屋有用過罷食吉野家，希望大家多多支持加藤屋","createTime":"2019-07-19T13:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T13:34:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":153,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"1e48cc62fb66590295209886f9360e3d16ec32da","tid":1332930,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:20:19.000Z","msg":"聽聞加藤屋晚市都座唔滿喎，你哋班友點搞架，又話支持加藤屋，又三分鐘熱度？？即將開嗰間唔知，起碼加藤屋一定係良心食店嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7iRYZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7iRYZC.jpg&h=a8df8db0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3c710386caab87ad6fa0ef5128c19e7d9da13c7","tid":1332930,"uid":22675,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0iKm9Qv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0iKm9Qv.png&h=4bd284d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張單寫住晚市優惠價，即係佢應該係夜晚食，晚市都座唔滿有無搞錯，係咪去咗食吉野家"},{"pid":"6d3d80126fe420540d5f7d95ad66358b91a1845a","tid":1332930,"uid":22675,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"最update 分店資料：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waE5UVc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaE5UVc.png&h=8508538e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U95QUyN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU95QUyN.png&h=01f7555c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wht3u7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWht3u7b.png&h=602f073f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1fef5c2be7d9486c0d547af5d39be96c3e2b7eb","tid":1332930,"uid":22675,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/csRgYDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcsRgYDg.png&h=6a5f177d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又平又抵 個班去吉